        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight">
            <span class="block text-white animate-slide-up">Hi, I'm</span>
            <span class="block bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 via-cyan-400 to-purple-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
              Alejandro
            </span>
            <span class="block text-white animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">Carrasco</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-gray-300 font-light animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.6s;">
            AI Researcher & Robotics Engineer at <span class="text-red-500 font-semibold">MIT</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 leading-relaxed animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.8s;">
          Specializing in <span class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">Large Language Models</span>, 
          <span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">autonomous agents</span>, and 
          <span class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold">robotics</span>. 
          Pushing the boundaries of AI to create intelligent systems that can reason, learn, and adapt.
